11#ifndef LOGGING_RTC_EVENT_LOG_EVENTS_RTC_EVENT_RTP_PACKET_OUTGOING_H_
12#define LOGGING_RTC_EVENT_LOG_EVENTS_RTC_EVENT_RTP_PACKET_OUTGOING_H_
13
14#include <cstddef>
15#include <cstdint>
16#include <memory>
17#include <utility>
18
19#include "api/array_view.h"
20#include "api/rtc_event_log/rtc_event.h"
21#include "modules/rtp_rtcp/source/rtp_packet.h"
22
23namespace webrtc {
24
25class RtpPacketToSend;
26
27class RtcEventRtpPacketOutgoing final : public RtcEvent {
28 public:
29 static constexpr Type kType = Type::RtpPacketOutgoing;
30
31 RtcEventRtpPacketOutgoing(const RtpPacketToSend& packet,
32 int probe_cluster_id);
33 ~RtcEventRtpPacketOutgoing() override;
34
35 Type GetType() const override { return kType; }
36 bool IsConfigEvent() const override { return false; }
37
38 std::unique_ptr<RtcEventRtpPacketOutgoing> Copy() const;
39
40 size_t packet_length() const { return packet_.size(); }
41
42 rtc::ArrayView<const uint8_t> RawHeader() const {
43 return rtc::MakeArrayView(packet_.data(), header_length());
44 }
45 uint32_t Ssrc() const { return packet_.Ssrc(); }
46 uint32_t Timestamp() const { return packet_.Timestamp(); }
47 uint16_t SequenceNumber() const { return packet_.SequenceNumber(); }
48 uint8_t PayloadType() const { return packet_.PayloadType(); }
49 bool Marker() const { return packet_.Marker(); }
50 template <typename ExtensionTrait, typename... Args>
51 bool GetExtension(Args&&... args) const {
52 return packet_.GetExtension<ExtensionTrait>(std::forward<Args>(args)...);
53 }
54 template <typename ExtensionTrait>
55 bool HasExtension() const {
56 return packet_.HasExtension<ExtensionTrait>();
57 }
58
59 size_t payload_length() const { return packet_.payload_size(); }
60 size_t header_length() const { return packet_.headers_size(); }
61 size_t padding_length() const { return packet_.padding_size(); }
62 int probe_cluster_id() const { return probe_cluster_id_; }
63
64 private:
65 RtcEventRtpPacketOutgoing(const RtcEventRtpPacketOutgoing& other);
66
67 const RtpPacket packet_;
68 // TODO(eladalon): Delete |probe_cluster_id_| along with legacy encoding.
69 const int probe_cluster_id_;
70};
71
72} // namespace webrtc
73
74#endif // LOGGING_RTC_EVENT_LOG_EVENTS_RTC_EVENT_RTP_PACKET_OUTGOING_H_
